1 Game Overview
Title: Last Man Alive
Platform: PC Standalone + iOS & Android, VR, XBox, Switch, 
Genre: Adventure/Survival
Rating: (10+) ESRB
Target: Casual gamer (aging from 12 - 30)
Serious games
Release date: Nov 2021
Publisher: Your Company Name
                                                                                   
Description: 
This is an adventure game where the player is the last human alive after a zombie apocalypse. He was trapped in his house alone and now must escape to a location where zombies cannot reach him; the ocean. He leaves his house and must not be caught by the zombies in order for him to reach his destination. Can you help him get there?
