7 Game Objectives
Jump over the zombies so u don’t get eaten. The game will get more difficult as time increases. Highest score will be recorded as the longest time it took for you to get caught by zombies. 
8 Game Rules
Must jump over all zombies. If touched or come within reach, game over.
